<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="68v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jacob Turner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l2"> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Jacob / vns iſt fürbraht 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd worden </del> vnd geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l4"> <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">einen den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l3">einen genant </ab></add> fricʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">en </del> von küngſſperg der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ıſt gefangen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_140_r2l5">habt </ab></add> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> / ob dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l7">alſo ſeẏ / daʒ Jr Jn <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ledig laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l9">wollet / Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nycolai </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="68v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jacob Turner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Jacob, uns ist
                                                fürbraht und gesagt <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                wie daz ir <add>einen, genant</add> Fricz von
                                                Küngssperg, der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ist, gefangen
                                                  <add>habt</add>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                                                ob dem also sey, daz ir in
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ledig lassen
                                                wollet, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                etc. <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> iiii
                                                  <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nycolai.</ab>
</div>
